      "raw_text": "James ]. Hill of the Great North\nern and George Slade. his son-m-law\nwill arrive in Spokane tomorrow\nThey are making a general tour of in\nspection, after the differences with\ntheir trainmen. They left cut Bank\nMont, today.\n\n\nr. C. Morgan, superintendent OF\nthe Spokane Falls 4 Northern, left\nin his private car this morning and\nwill go as far as IIavre to meet his\nwife. They will reside here."
